Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Metal Branding
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.83,0:21:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,吃了兩發Maximum攻擊 居然毫髮無傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.77,0:21:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他散發著何等程度的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,明明我都用了W最高熱強勁的Heat Metal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真是 可怕的強敵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這才是準幹部嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.62,0:21:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可別瞧不起人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我還沒獲得驅動器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.69,0:21:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但我是要繼承萬燈先生的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.73,0:22:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,又到了 裡風都
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不好 得趕緊逃才行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用這麼害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.57,0:22:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡不是你的家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.49,0:22:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是很想你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,時芽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.82,0:24:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,參雜體妄想日記
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.76,0:24:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,如果 裡風都參雜體是一支搖滾樂團的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.57,0:24:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你們幾個參雜體要組樂隊也太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.91,0:24:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Reactor太熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.03,0:24:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Brachiosaurus個頭太大
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.23,0:24:49.38,Top,,0,0,0,,喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.62,0:24:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Scream太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.89,0:24:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不過
